p/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1419_4.0.0.xml#_eea79623-bc7d-4ef1-b787-8452b6383ffc" id="_10bd7f04-627e-47ec-a378-dc7ce72272f3" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">public corridor</xref> or the like leading to an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_73f7b40e-5055-489b-8fb1-c7894bac2a05" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>; and</li><li id="_4967738a-c335-403d-8198-f2a20e6acc42">externally above every doorway opening to a road or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1385_0.4.0.xml#_b4a20ca6-0197-4381-9e50-85c757fa574f" id="_0e1377e4-9c2d-4b27-959f-e777baaec11b" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">open space</xref>; and</li><li id="_aaf81bb2-b863-40fc-9315-0686b108e12c">in any <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_0bd94387-0a57-4795-b3d0-a339b9271eaa" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> of the building if illumination sufficient for safe egress will not be available under conditions of emergency.</li></ol></subclause></clause>